title: Tin Foil Hat #65: Space X with Eddie Bravo
description:
Thank you for tuning into another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode Ryan and Sam welcome Eddie Bravo to talk Space X. This episode we discuss.....
1) Tin Foil Hat Comedy Night live Feb 23rd and 24th at the LA Comedy Club at 11:30pm. Tickets are available at TheLAComedyClub.com.
2)Satanism and Rock and Roll
3)Nikola Tesla
4) The Black Knight Satellite
5) Elon Musk
6) Space X
7) Ryan shows Eddie a clip of Joey Diaz talking about how he convinced Eddie that Rogan is in the CIA.
8) Eddie shoot Ryan a death stare!
9) Sam fears for his life!
10) Ryan shits his pants.
All of this and more on a fun episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. Thank you for all of your support.
